name: Dianna L. CABLE, Petitioner, v. Emmanuel S. ANTHOU, Respondent

parties: Dianna L. CABLE, Petitioner, v. Emmanuel S. ANTHOU, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM:
AND NOW, this 9th day of October, 1996, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is granted and limited to the following issue:
May a trial court order a second buccal swab DNA test when there is no evidence that the first test was defective?
opinions.author: PER CURIAM:

casebody.head_matter:
683 A.2d 290
Dianna L. CABLE, Petitioner, v. Emmanuel S. ANTHOU, Respondent.
No. 287 Western District Allocatur 1996.
Supreme Court of Pennsylvania.
Oct. 9, 1996.
Kevin J. McKeon, for Petitioner.
